<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="342" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,253,2033]" pageId="11" pageNumber="342">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1971,1997]" pageId="11" pageNumber="342">Etymology.</emphasis>
The epithet of the new species is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[964,1030,1972,1997]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="342">ventr-</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[1084,1180,1972,1997]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="342">spinosus</emphasis>
, referring to the spines along the ventral margin of the valva.
</paragraph>
